I remember my favorite question from my first-ever CS course. How do you remove all elements from a stack?

Incorrect:
while (stack->top) { 
    stack->pop();
}

Correct:
stack->top = 0;

Probably the first time I saw what an "elegant solution" looked like in computing. Loved it!

